OL,3,CIs the UK able to defend itself and
OL,4,Cwhat's at stake in the local elections?
OL,6,FWatch the latest edition of Around the
OL,7,FHouse from Thursday 16 April
OL,9,FClaims from the former head of NATO
OL,10,FLord Robertson that UK is ''under-
OL,11,Fprepared'' and ''in peril'' have hit
OL,12,Fthe headlines this week, with the
OL,13,Fconflict in the Middle East also
OL,14,Fraising questions about the state of
OL,15,FBritain's military.
