OL,3,CIs the UK able to defend itself and
OL,4,Cwhat's at stake in the local elections?
OL,6,FDeep-fried and processed food is on
OL,7,Fthe way out for school meals,
OL,8,Ffollowing the government announcement
OL,9,Fthat more fruit and veg are to go on
OL,10,Fschool lunch menus, to reduce obesity
OL,11,Fand tooth decay.
OL,13,FThe panel give their reaction to a
OL,14,Fshake-up of school meals - as do some
OL,15,Fof the people we stopped to speak to
OL,16,Fin Carlisle
OL,18,FThe next edition of Around The House
OL,19,Fis on Thursday 14 May.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/4
